doc.after: Marcus Fabius Quintilianus c 35 c 100 CE was a Roman rhetorician from Hispania widely referred to in medieval schools of rhetoric and in Renaissance writing In English translation he is usually referred to as Quintilian kw n t lj n i n although the alternate spellings of Quintillian and Quinctilian are occasionally seen the latter in older texts 1
